	                  <tr class="text_title">
	                    <td align="left">Optimal Operation  of Health, Safety, Environment &amp; Quality (HSEQ) System</td>
	                  </tr>
	                  <tr>
	                    <td align="left">Through diligent implementation of  our HSEQ system, KNOC achieved a no-disaster/no-accident record
	at most of its worksites. Moreover,  we have ensured the smooth promotion of key our businesses by
	meeting all domestic and  international standards.</td>
	                  </tr>
	                  <tr class="text_title">
	                    <td align="left">Saving Energy  &amp; Resources</td>
	                  </tr>
	                  <tr>
	                    <td align="left">KNOC has reduced annual energy  &amp; resources consumption each year, and has met annual targets despite
	an overall increase in equipment  and facilities.</td>
	                  </tr>
	                  <tr class="text_title">
	                    <td align="left">Selected as  Superior Energy-Saving Agency</td>
	                  </tr>
	                  <tr>
	                    <td align="left">Thanks to our efforts to enhance  energy conservation awareness and practice, KNOC was selected as a ¡°superior¡±  energy-saving agency
	through government joint  inspections in 2006. In addition, personnel in charge of energy conservation  won a special commendation from the
	Minister of Commerce, Industry and  Energy at the 28th Energy-Saving Promotion Event.</td>
	                  </tr>
	                  <tr class="text_title">
	                    <td align="left">Efforts to Protect  Sea &amp; Water Quality</td>
	                  </tr>
	                  <tr>
	                    <td align="left">In consideration of the impact our  key businesses have on sea and water quality, KNOC sets strict internal targets  and chieves them. Moreover,
	to prevent oil spills,  comprehensive countermeasures for morning oil tankers were announced in April 2007.</td>
	                  </tr>
	                  <tr class="text_title">
	                    <td align="left">Coping with  Climate Change</td>
	                  </tr>
	                  <tr>
	                    <td align="left">We are concerned about the mounting  environmental problems pf global warning and ozone layer depletion. Thus, KNOC  shares awareness on environmental pollution that can  occur during the construction of terminals at storage facilities, and we study  ways to make improvements on the
	environmental front.</td>
	                  </tr>
