	                  <tr>
	                    <td height="30" align="left"><img src="../images/sub02/conttext_27.gif" width="416" height="23" alt="KNOC Chosen as Superior Energy-Saving Public Institution" /></td>
	                    <td width="210" rowspan="3" align="right" valign="bottom"><img src="../images/sub02/img22.jpg" width="183" height="190" alt="" /></td>
	                  </tr>
	                  <tr align="left">
	                    <td>offices and operated a reduced  number of elevators according to time slot. Moreover, we carried out  energy-conservation education and checks at storage bases and construction  offices. KNOC was selected as an &quot;outstanding&quot; energy-saving agency after  the 2006 government joint inspection. In addition, KNOC¡¯s energy personnel won  a commendation from the Minister of Commerce, Industry and Energy at an energy  conservation promotion event.</td>
	                    </tr>
	                  <tr align="left">
	                    <td class="text_title">[December 2006]</td>
